title: Ep. 404 - Socialist Fight!
description:
Sanders and Warren are at each other's throats. I have no dog in the fight, but it should be noted that Warren is a known liar. Also, another journalist is assaulted by a raging SJW. And a college professor explains why it's racist for white people to ask for evidence before they believe a claim. Finally, following JK Rowling's lead, Stephen King just got himself canceled.
